name: Natural Option
description:
Natural Option photo retouching and editing. Perfect if you want your photograph to look untouched.

We’ll carefully blend away any imperfections and blemishes and soften and reduce fine lines or wrinkles. But we won't hide your moles or freckles or change your face or body shape. No one will suspect a thing. You can see some before and after examples on our gallery page.

The Natural Option includes:

Lighting & colour balance correction
Red eye removal 
Dark circle removal from eyes 
Eye brightening 
Teeth whitening (natural) 
Blemish removal (face & body) 
Fine line & wrinkle reduction 
Hair refinement 
Removal of stains & creases from clothing

name: Superstar Option
description:
Superstar Option photo retouching and editing. The full on superstar airbrush treatment. 

The Superstar package includes all the airbrushing a photograph would receive before it is featured on the pages of a glossy magazine. We painstakingly remove any imperfections using a variety of retouching techniques. You can see some before and after examples on our gallery page.

Superstar option includes:

Lighting & colour balance correction 
Red eye removal 
Dark circle removal from eyes 
Eye brightening 
Teeth whitening (natural) 
Blemish removal (face & body) 
Fine line & wrinkle reduction 
Hair refinement 
Removal of stains & creases from clothing 
Teeth straightening 
Face shape refinement 
slimming and smoothing 
Body shape refinement 
slimming and smoothing 
Superstar Tan 
Superstar glow 
Superstar make-up 
Background retouching

name: Mix Option
description:
Mix Option photo retouching and editing. Mix and match individual treatments for the perfect retouching package for your photos.

The mix option includes all of the individual treatments we offer, from simple red-eye removal to full on superstar glow. You can see some before and after examples on our gallery page.

If you would like to select more than one treatment please contact us for a quote. The cost is £2.50 per treatment but with a minimum cost of £5.00.
